description: Southern Pitch is serving you a delicious taste of history! Comfort food you can feel good about--these healthier variations on old recipes will leave you feeling satisfied. More than just fantastic food though, Southern Pitch is a mobile tribute to the history of the Negro Leagues Baseball players & teams. Learning about an important part of recent history while also chowing down on some excellent food - what could be better than that?
name: Southern Pitch Food Truck
